dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Sauk County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NSauk_Roads_ROW_2018.gdbN. [This feature class contains detailed line work supporting Sauk Counties road network and contains street name, classification, and address range attributes. The primary division of a simultaneous conveyance and generally referred to as lots, units, or common elements.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
